            It’s Not Information Sharing—It's Surveillance
          %a{href: "https://act.eff.org/action/stop-the-cyber-bills"}
            %span.link-div.hidden-xs
          %a.btn.btn-lg.btn-red.visible-xs{href: "https://act.eff.org/action/stop-the-cyber-bills"}
            Take action

